definitions.definition: A woman, especially an attractive one, skilled at using magic ; an alluring witch .
A beautiful , charming and irresistible woman.
examples: She was the enchantress of men’s hearts.
His desire for that enchantress led him to financial ruin.

main_definition: A woman, especially an attractive one, skilled at using magic ; an alluring witch .
secondary_definitions: A beautiful , charming and irresistible woman.
